IMC
Integrated medical care
OVERVIEW
It is a system that was invented to help the medical staff, but under their
supervision, as it contributed to reducing the burden on doctors in cases
of extreme pressure, and developing health care. This system is a
medical robot that was created based on the field of artificial intelligence,
machine learning, and the field of Robotics, as this robot predicts the
diagnosis of some diseases, including diabetes and some types of
cancer, which helps in early diagnosis, ease of detecting the disease in its
early stages, and ease of treatment. It also measures some of the
patients? vital signs, which are body temperature, sugar, and heartbeat.
This was done using some medical sensors. This was aimed at providing
medical care to patients in the event of epidemics or cases of infectious
disease. It was also used to help people with special needs carry out
daily tasks, alert them to the timing of medication, and provide them with
health care.
PROBLEM STATEMENT
Due to the recent spread of diseases and epidemics, such as
Covid-19, which has negatively affected medical care and early
diagnosis of diseases, which has led to the disease progressing
in its final stages and thus becoming difficult to treat. For some
diseases, such as cancer, delay in discovering them causes
death, and also causes pressure on the medical worker. This led
to pressure on hospitals and doctors, and they faced the risk of
death and fatigue, which led to unintentional human errors.
There were some people suffering from difficulty in accessing
medical care, whether due to long distances, time constraints, or
a lack of health resources in some areas.
